Nh6 {[%cal Yh6f7]} 11. Bc2 c6 12. h3 $5 {[%csl Yd4,Rd7,Rg7,Rh6] Black doesn't
have enough pressure against d4, so we can keep the tension in the center.} (
12. d5 c5 {[%cal Gf6f5,Yh6f7,Yg7h6] makes it easier for Black to achieve his
