because of} 17. Qxe7 Nxe7 18. Nb5 {[%csl Rd6]} Be5 19. Be4 $18 {[%csl Gd1,Rd6]
which is why we put the rook on d1 in the first place.}) 16. Rf3 $14 {[%csl
